org.coode.owlapi.manchesterowlsyntax

Interface ManchesterOWLSyntaxParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ManchesterOWLSyntaxEditorParser

    public interface ManchesterOWLSyntaxParser
    Interface for a parser able to parse Manchester OWL Syntax. This covers Protege use of the parser.
    Author:
    ignazio
